import apiURL from'../APIconfig';import axios from'axios';// Get All Ticket
export var getAllTicket=function getAllTicket(){return axios.get("".concat(apiURL,"/emp/allTickets"));};// Get ALl Emp SendTickets By Emp ID
export var getEmpSendTickets=function getEmpSendTickets(id){return axios.get("".concat(apiURL,"/emp/SendTickets/").concat(id));};// Get ALl Emp ReceivedTickets By Emp ID
export var getreceivedTickets=function getreceivedTickets(id){return axios.get("".concat(apiURL,"/emp/ReceivedTickets/").concat(id));};//close Ticket 
export var closeTicket=function closeTicket(id){return axios({method:'patch',url:apiURL+"/UpdateTicket/".concat(id),data:{TicketState:'closed'}});};//delete Ticket 
export var deleteTicket=function deleteTicket(id){return axios({method:'delete',url:apiURL+"/DeleteTicket/".concat(id)});};//Add new Employee
export var AddNewEmployee=function AddNewEmployee(req){return axios({method:'POST',url:apiURL+'/emp/register',data:{empFullName:req.empFullName,email:req.email,empUsername:req.empUsername,password:req.password,empPhone:req.empPhone}});};//Add new Tickect 
export var AddNewTicket=function AddNewTicket(req,id){return axios({method:'POST',url:apiURL+"/".concat(id),data:{TicketType:req.TicketType,TicketDescription:req.TicketDescription,TicketState:req.TicketState}});};//Update Ticket 
export var UpdateTicket=function UpdateTicket(req,id){return axios({method:'patch',url:apiURL+"/UpdateTicket/".concat(id),data:{TicketDescription:req.TicketDescription,TicketState:req.TicketState}});};
